uild\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123204\/things-to-do-langkawi-malaysia-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123204\/things-to-do-langkawi-malaysia-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Best Things To Do in Langkawi (3-Day Travel Guide)\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There are a few different routes you can take to reach the falls, depending on whether you prefer a shorter or longer hike, but if you can&#x2019;t make it to the falls you can also see it from the cable car on your way up to the sky bridge.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/langkawi-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all hotels in Langkawi<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123301\/langkawi-seven-wells-pools-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi seven wells pools\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"langkawi seven wells pools\" data-id=\"19573\" data-full-url=