class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123258\/langkawi-Seven-Wells-Waterfall.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Relax at Pantai Cenang<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>After a busy day, chill and see the sunset at one of the island&#x2019;s most beautiful beaches. Pantai Cenang is well located on the west side of the island, where most cafes\/restaurants\/music bars are located. The long stretch of white sand spans for 2km and is the most popular beach on the island, which makes for a lively, fun atmosphere.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also discover:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/malaysia\/penang-georgetown\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Georgetown, Penang<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123227\/langkawi-Cenang-Beach-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi Cenang Beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"langkawi Cenang Beach\" data-id=\"19588\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123227\/langkawi-Cenang-