K4jtMnwBVEUp6\" target=\"_blank\">Temoyong Night Market<\/a><\/li><li>Fri: <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/2MgnqmBVkRVEqb7c9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Ayer Hangat Night Market (opens in a new tab)\">Ayer Hangat Night Market<\/a><\/li><li>Sat: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Kuah Night Market (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/nuYK4rAG7gNy4AMC7\" target=\"_blank\">Kuah Night Market<\/a><\/li><li>Sun: <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/HD5eYgG86A4XgHFM7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Padang Matsirat Night Market (opens in a new tab)\">Padang Matsirat Night Market<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-1007x810.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"420\" height=\"338\" alt=\"langkawi market\" class=\"wp-image-19606 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1007px) 100vw, 1007px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-1007x810.jpg 1007w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-300x241.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-600x483.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-746x600.jpg 746w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-420x338.jpg 420w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-1536x1236.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123207\/langkawi-market-163x131.jp