Langkawi&#x2019;s northeast coastline is covered with dense mangrove forest and is incredibly important for the island&#x2019;s ecosystem. The Mangrove is a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO<\/a> Global Geopark, in other words: a protected area that can only be visited by taking a boat tour. A mangrove tour is a great way to learn about plants and wildlife and how they all work together in the ecosystem.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/langkawi-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all hotels in Langkawi<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123355\/Langkawi-Mangrove-tour-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Langkawi Mangrove tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Langkawi Mangrove tour\" data-id=\"19484\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123355\/Langkawi-Mangrove-tour.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=19484\" class=\"wp-image-19484 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uplo