ner\">\n<p>Get your adrenaline pumping by zipping across the 12 zip lines in the Langkawi jungle. The longest zipline of Langkawi is located at the foot of the Seven Wells Waterfall. It gives a spectacular view of both the waterfall and jungle.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/langkawi-zipline\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Book your tour here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book your zipline experience here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"boattour\">9. Sunset boat tour<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most popular things to do in Langkawi is to take one of the many boat tours that are on offer around the island. A range of cruises is available, such as island-hop on and off cruises, luxury sunset cruises, and mangrove tours. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123342\/things-to-do-langkawi-sunset-cruise.jpg\" alt=\"things to do langkawi sunset cruise\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do langkawi sunset cruise\" class=\"wp-image-19496 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123342\/things-to-do-langkawi-sunset-cruise.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/2312334