:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-30x19.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-163x102.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-289x180.jpg 289w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-768x479.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-1024x638.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-1440x898.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia-30x19.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123345\/eagle-langkawi-malaysia.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The second activity is to feed the eagles (normally a part of the island hopping tour). Travelers are encouraged to feed the eagles chicken skin, which is not a part of their natural diet, resulting in an imbalance of the food chain that causes damage to the ecosystem. Never support activities that use animals in this way and trust your instincts as to which activities may be inhumane.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Book onto a mangrove tour instead, where you can see beautiful birds and other wildlife in their natural environment, without causing them damage through feeding.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"tropical island malaysia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"tropical island malaysia\" class=\"wp-image-19576 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123251\/tropical-island-malaysia-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up