ngkawi. The journey is about 2-3 hours but it is worth checking the weather, as during the monsoon season the crossing can be rough.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/ferry\/george-town\/langkawi\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your Super Fast Ferry tickets here<\/a> (search for a date to see ferries)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi ferry malaysia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"langkawi ferry malaysia\" class=\"wp-image-19600 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-malaysia-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123221\/langkawi-ferry-ma