sunnycars-en-malaysia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>&#xA0;as they work with local car rental companies. When booking through Sunny Cars, the price already includes all insurances.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-malaysia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi malaysia rice paddies\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"315\" alt=\"langkawi malaysia rice paddies\" class=\"wp-image-19583 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-600x419.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-800x559.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-1080x755.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-450x315.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-1536x1074.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123238\/langkawi-malaysia-rice-paddies-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltino