     <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/langkawi\/koh-lipe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Get your ferry tickets here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get your ferry tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"restaurants\">Restaurants in Langkawi<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a wide selection of restaurants spread over the island. A mix of Malay and middle eastern cuisine are most common. These were our favorites:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g298283-d5000128-Reviews-Yasmin_Restaurant-Langkawi_Langkawi_District_Kedah.html\">Yasmin Syrian Restaurant<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g298283-d3261856-Reviews-Haroo_Haroo_Korean_Restaurant-Langkawi_Langkawi_District_Kedah.html\">Haroo Korean Restaurant<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g298283-d6983469-Reviews-The_Kasbah-Langkawi_Langkawi_District_Kedah.html\">The Kasbah<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g1096277-d10722095-Reviews-Arts_Cafe_Langkawi-Kuah_Langkawi_Langkawi_District_Kedah.html\">Arts Cafe Langkawi<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tripadvisor.nl\/Restaurant_Review-g298283-d866767-Reviews-The_Loaf_Perdana_Quay-Langkawi_Langkawi_District_Kedah.html\">The Loaf Bakery &amp; Bistro<\/a><\/li><li>Night markets<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/23123157\/langkawi-malaysia-best-restaurant-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"langkawi malaysia best restaurant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"langkawi malaysia best restaurant\" data-id=\"19616\" da